data.description: Better, Bigger, and good condition. Nice sq footage, 2 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, plus a loft that can be used as tv room, office, or playarea for children, Carpet upstairs, Wood Laminate flooring downstairs in living room, kitchen and entry area, ceiling fans, central air conditioning, smart lights downstairs, new backsplash in kitchen and bar area. This one has patio with a little garden area to plant roses or veggies, or just sit out for a quiet evening. Mountain Views, and close to military bases. Come see its a beautiful townhome
